Loamie is a Multi-User Dungeon engine written in Java, though it is currently
lacking a combat system.

Features
  *	Support for an arbitrary number of simultaneous players
  *	World can be edited live, in-game: create, edit and delete rooms/objects on-the-fly.
  *	Load and save world as easy-to-edit XML files
  *	Minor scripting engine
  *	Server configuration read from XML file

Improvements
  *	Authentication, Passwords and Permissions
  *	Combat Engine

Known Bugs
  *	Does not load/display world welcome and goodbye messages

